
NAME
    Log - Loggen van berichten naar de log-server.

DESCRIPTION
    De log package geeft functies om berichten te sturen naar de log
    server.

SYNOPSIS

    use log;

    log_info ( $progname, $message )
       
	logt $message naar log file $progname met severity LOG_INFO.

    log_warning ( $progname, $message )
       
	logt $message naar log file $progname met severity LOG_WARN.

    log_error ( $progname, $message )
       
	logt $message naar log file $progname met severity LOG_ERR.

    log_fatal ( $progname, $message )
       
	logt $message naar log file $progname met severity LOG_FATAL.


AUTHORS

    Hans Dijkema

                            =====================

HOW TO INSTALL IT ?

To install this module, cd to the directory that contains this README
file and type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make test
    make install

To install this module into a specific directory, do:
perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=/name/of/the/directory
...the rest is the same...

Please also read the perlmodinstall man page, if available.

Share and Enjoy !!

